snippet.title: Peach Clicker // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3125030/Peach_Clicker/

You've clicked on so many bananas, but have you clicked on peaches? 🤔 In Peach Clicker you smack a Peach to get even more Peaches! 😍 Every 3 hours, you get a new peach! 🍑 Come smack some peaches with us!

Developed by
Event Horizon Ltd
